strings.Value: "I was just passing by. Good work!"
"I changed my mind. I'll come back later."
"Look, it's {mf|King|Queen} {Name}! Forgive me, Your Highness, but you can't go in there! Irovetti's orders!"
"Look who's here! {mf|King|Queen} {Name}! Is {mf|he|she} really going to give up the crown just like that?"
"All is quiet, Your Highness! Couldn't be better!"
"Forgive us, but we can't! His Highness Irovetti gave strict instructions!"
"What's keeping you? The gate is open! Come in, Your Highness — His Highness has been expecting you, Your, um... Highness!" {n}The guard scratches his head, confused with the 'highnesses'.{/n}
"Of course! Of course! The moment our King invites you — please return right away!"
"As you wish. But King Irovetti is expecting you!"
